Titolo: The Adventures of Valdo & Marie

Anno: 1996

Descrizione: The Adventures of Valdo & Marie is a 1996 adventure educational video game for Windows by Ubi Soft Entertainment Software.
PC Team praised the game's commitment to being an educational historical adventure. Joystick felt it offered a beautiful experience to players. Personal Computer Magazine thought the game offered a "highly entertaining learning environment".The game sold 100,000 copies in France alone.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
